test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7cb7dc16f840>([-57])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7cb7dc16f840> = [[1], [1, -57], [-57, 1], [-57, 1, -57], [1], [1, -57], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -19 == -57
 +  where -19 = <built-in function prod>([-19])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
